Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.81,0:11:03.62,英黑,,0,0,0,,I look at the gray beard, Tracy says, I've seen a lot of things.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.65,0:11:06.88,英黑,,0,0,0,,You never know. You never know, young man. Keep driving.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.46,英黑,,0,0,0,,Fast forward to recently, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.49,0:11:12.06,英黑,,0,0,0,,I think about that conversation a lot.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.50,英黑,,0,0,0,,I think about that conversation a lot.
