Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.03,0:11:48.72,英黑,,0,0,0,,I got my dad a present for Father's Day, and this got weird.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.75,0:11:54.46,英黑,,0,0,0,,I uploaded this to the internet, and I was taking guidance and control classes here.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.96,英黑,,0,0,0,,I got him a chicken. It's a chicken.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.26,英黑,,0,0,0,,I got my dad a chicken.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.28,0:12:02.26,英黑,,0,0,0,,I started looking at it, and I was like, there's some GNC stuff going on here.
