Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.20,0:12:18.38,英黑,,0,0,0,,The chickens are really good at this. I'll show you. Watch his head stay totally stationary. [Audience Laughs]
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.41,0:12:26.96,英黑,,0,0,0,,You guys are super nerdy, so I know where your brain's going right now. You're going to the pigeon guided bomb in the world.
