Dialogue: 1,0:56:36.72,0:56:38.94,英黑,,0,0,0,,You felt it, didn't you? Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:38.96,0:56:41.46,英黑,,0,0,0,,Nobody else in the room knows what it is. Try it again.
